---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import regisImage from '../assets/images/regis.png';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Simple dark background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy-black"></div>

  <!-- Enhanced floating elements for depth -->
  <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-500/25 rounded-full blur-3xl float-slow"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-80 h-80 bg-emerald-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl float-medium"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 w-48 h-48 bg-pink-500/30 rounded-full blur-2xl float-fast"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Photo section with intro badge -->
      <div class="animate-slide-left relative pb-14">
        <Image 
          src={regisImage} 
          alt="Régis ROLNIN, Expert en croissance PME et créateur de la Méthode AIA™"
          class="w-full h-auto object-contain transition-all duration-500"
          loading="lazy"
          width="800"
          height="1000"
          quality={95}
        />

        <!-- Intro badge (glass) -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
          <span
            class="glass inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-white/95 border border-white/20 shadow-xl"
            aria-label="Bonjour, je suis Régis."
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5.121 17.804A13.937 13.937 0 0112 15c2.5 0 4.847.655 6.879 1.804M15 10a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="font-semibold">Bonjour, je suis <span class="text-amber-300">Régis</span>.</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Premium glassmorphism content section -->
      <div class="animate-slide-right" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class="glass-strong p-10 rounded-3xl hover-lift transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 glass rounded-full mb-8">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-3 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-amber-400">Votre Guide Expert</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-8 font-crimson">
            Je comprends vos défis de
            <span class="text-gradient-gold block">dirigeant de PME.</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-8 text-xl text-gray-300 font-crimson mb-10">
            <p class="leading-relaxed font-crimson">
              Entre pression administrative, gestion des équipes et des locaux, faire croître votre activité devient vite une source de charge mentale continue — et de journées à rallonge.
            </p>
            
            <p class="leading-relaxed font-crimson">
              C’est parce que j’ai vécu ces mêmes frustrations que j’ai conçu la Méthode AIA™ : un cadre simple et structurant, pour vous aider à reprendre la main sur le développement de votre activité — marketing et opérationnel — sans complexité inutile.
            </p>

            <!-- Premium trust indicator with glassmorphism -->
            <div class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-gold-500/50">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gold-500 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="font-bold text-gold-400 text-xl font-crimson">
                  Issu de plus de 10 ans d’expérience terrain, validé par des dirigeants de PME ambitieuses.
                </p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gold-300 font-semibold font-crimson">
                Un plan structuré pour générer des résultats progressifs dès 90 jours.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Premium glassmorphism buttons -->
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6">
            <a
              href="/travailler-avec-moi"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 cta-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover-lift transition-all duration-300 text-lg"
            >
              Parlons de votre projet
              <svg class="ml-3 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            
            <a
              href="/a-propos"
              class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 cta-secondary-dark text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover-lift transition-all duration-300 text-lg"
            >
              Qui suis-je ?
              <svg class="ml-3 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
